IMPORTANT GENERAL INFORMATION
AIR FREIGHT
Personalized "hot Pack" Service, Airport to Airport
Freight $11.00 minimum per shipment. Rate 14 cents Ib., plus 5 per cent
Federal Tax.
BAGGAGE
Free allowance is 40 pounds, including brief case and hand luggage. Excess
baggage may be accepted, space and weight permitting and will be charged
at the rate of 14 cents per pound, $2.00 minimum.
CHECK-IN TIME FOR FLIGHTS
In the interest of on time service to all passengers, please be at the airport
counter 20 minutes prior to scheduled flight time. Reservations not claimed 20
minutes prior to scheduled flight time are subject to cancellation.
PAYMENTS
In addition to cash, SKYSTREAM accepts Master Charge, Bank-Americard,
Carte Blanche, Diners Club, Interbank, American Express credit cards.
WEATHER DELAYS OR CANCELLATIONS
SKYSTREAM AIRLINES will not be responsible for passengers travel or
overnight expenses when flights are delayed or cancelled due to weather. The
passenger will receive space on the first available fliaht. or the unused
portion of the ticket will be refunded.
